{"tid":1684381,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"行動post，11月8日再唔回應訴求，第二日「推倒圍牆」宣佈成立新政府","createTime":"2019-10-31T05:09:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T08:57:28.000Z","uid":177168,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4dae82f47ba34a8638b87c0469ea30de64bf5283","tid":1684381,"uid":177168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T05:09:38.000Z","msg":"當日要全民三罷，早上開始佔領所有政府建築物，以及電視台，可以仿傚10月4臨時政府宣言，宣佈現有政府為非法組織予以取締，理據是中英聯合聲明不讓港人當年自決，是建基於中國強行於1972年在聯大把港澳剔出非自治領土。中國威脅英國無法協助香港獨立。現在是港人行使聯合國1514號決議《給予殖民地國家和人民獨立宣言》，將過去22年列為被中國殖民時期。外援方面，暗中通知英美派兵守住空海陸三路。至於選舉方面，由「香港臨時政府籌備委員會」主導，盡快於90日內舉行「獨立」及區議院、立法院、總統選舉，以及接收所有現有政府部門，廢除1997年7月1日起的法例變更。執行憲法 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1327495/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1327495/page/1</a>。<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"ffaa2a9da87b39297f19ea799502ed7c64ab677b","tid":1684381,"uid":177168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T05:13:01.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c59fbcdcd9427551644d37dfd365bbd4e91a1d11","tid":1684381,"uid":279356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T05:16:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/04EdLjM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F04EdLjM.gif&h=e7e4e8ef&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"662011d497e27bfba69353a5bc895280af8adb47","tid":1684381,"uid":48987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T05:16:36.000Z","msg":"參考85罷工 五區集會 討論<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1684174\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1684174</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"bf1629ca120cf2818c0b0da28a89cbab44db4d53","tid":1684381,"uid":177168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T05:20:21.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"96ac394905528fa72e6fb8d8aabfa8f343174fb5","tid":1684381,"uid":177168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T05:37:24.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"43a37429343f1723351f6774a12cca63eed6